last_episode_to_air.name: Bike Buddies Super Speedy Delivery Service

name: Ricky Zoom
overview: Little red rescue motorbike Ricky Zoom, along with his loyal and enthusiastic bike buddies Loop, Scootio and DJ, race around the sports track, try new stunts at the park, and zoom into adventures.

episodes.name: Ricky Wobbles
episodes.overview: Ricky and the buddies are performing at Steel Awesome Fest.

episodes.name: The Out of Controller
episodes.overview: The Bike Buddies recreate a remote controller from a Steel Awesome movie.

episodes.name: Flat Out Awesome
episodes.overview: Loop gets a flat tire on the way to a Steel Awesome stunt show, so Ricky and the Buddies decide to pull him to the show on a trailer. But when they find Loop has fallen off the trailer, they put their friend before the show and retrace their tracks.

episodes.name: The Most Amazing Thing Put in a Box Ever
episodes.overview: Worried that he always messes things up, Loop is determined to be true to his word and follow his dad's instructions to not open a new parcel he is helping his dad to deliver. When the parcel gets knocked, it splits open to reveal an amazing Vroomboard.

episodes.name: New Bike On the Block
episodes.overview: Ricky starts pretending to be someone he's not when his friends seem to prefer his cousin Dasher over him.

episodes.name: The Wheelford Wheeler
episodes.overview: Maxwell tells the buddies about the famous masked rescue racer The Wheelford Wheeler.

episodes.name: Problem at Windshield Point
episodes.overview: Scootio's tablet stops working when there is a storm in Wheelford, so the buddies ride to the top of Windshield Point to help her. They find the big satellite dish is broken and Ricky and Loop climb to the top of the satellite tower to fix the dish.

episodes.name: Super Awesome Magnet
episodes.overview: The Buddies are using Maxwell's super magnet to gather metal for a super ramp. When they get over excited with the magnet, they touch too many buttons and set the magnet on an unstoppable course around Wheelford.

episodes.name: Ricky's on a Roll
episodes.overview: Ricky is going to help DJ and his parents at the adventure park but becomes side-tracked by the new Bike Sphere. While Ricky races around the inside of the sphere the door lever jams and Ricky gets stuck inside.

episodes.name: Wheeloween
episodes.overview: Ricky and his friends think that a ghost walks to Wheelford during the traditional Wheeloween house tour.

episodes.name: Zoom Encounters
episodes.overview: Ricky and friends think that a ghost is driving around Wheelford during Wheelo-ween trick or treat; Maxwell and the buddies believe that aliens are visiting Wheelford.

episodes.name: SantaCycle Down
episodes.overview: Ricky and the buddies meet Santa Cycle, who has crash-landed in Wheelford on Christmas Eve and needs to capture the magic of Christmas to get back into the sky.

episodes.name: Ruled by Ricky
episodes.overview: Officer Bunker puts Ricky and his buddies in charge of patrolling the bike park and, most importantly, his fun balloon stand during the Wheelford Fair. At first, Ricky and his buddies take their responsibilities very seriously.

episodes.name: Blip in Charge
episodes.overview: Ricky and the buddies help Blip to become a good leader in an Easter Egg hunt.

episodes.name: Loop Hero of Wheelford
episodes.overview: Loop starts to believe that he is a real rescue bike and takes it too far.

episodes.name: Maxwell Gets a Little Help
episodes.overview: Ricky and the buddies help Maxwell at the garage when he sprains his spokes. They soon realize it's not as easy as it looks when they help a huge line of bikes which all need repairs.

episodes.name: Ricky's Litter Round Up
episodes.overview: After accidentally throwing out his dad's precious emergency light, Ricky must recover it with the help of Scootio, DJ and Loop.

episodes.name: Slippy Street
episodes.overview: Ricky is earning his good deed badge and sets up a bike wash. He doesn't follow instructions from Maxwell and soon the bikes are slipping around Wheelford.

episodes.name: Bike Buddies Super Speedy Delivery Service
